---
import SocialLinks from './SocialLinks.astro';
import OtherLinks from './OtherLinks.astro';

import {
  NAME,
  ROLE,
} from '../consts';
---
<section class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between sm:space-x-8 mt-4">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 items-center">
    <img
      fetchpriority="high"
      src="https://github.com/MattTheTekie.png"
      alt="MattTheTekie's GitHub avatar"
      class="rounded-lg mx-auto mt-4 mb-2"
      width="256"
      height="256"
    />
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2 text-center sm:text-justify">Social Links</h3>
    <SocialLinks/>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:items-start sm:justify-start mt-4 sm:mt-0">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold my-4 p-2 bg-blue-600 w-fit" transition:animate="slide">
      Hi, I'm {NAME}!
    </h1>
    <p class="my-4 text-justify">
      I'm a 21-year-old <b>{ROLE}</b> based in America with a strong focus in reverse engineering. I'm the creator of the Venith Network podcast series. I maintain scripts for various projects such as the <a href="https://gitlab.com/suyu-emu/suyu" class="text-blue-500" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">suyu emulator</a>, <a href="https://github.com/VenithNET/streetpass-shop" class="text-blue-500" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The StreetPass-Shop for the 3DS</a>,<a href="https://discord.com/invite/cX6nvUUA2T" class="text-blue-500" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Reviive Shop for the Wii</a>, the closed-alpha Homebrew-eShop for the 3DS, and I am currently working on infrastructure as a hobby.
    </p>
    <p class="my-4 text-justify">
      In my free time, I indulge in <a href="https://home.venith.net/projects/" class="text-blue-500" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">maintaining infrastructure</a>, <a href="https://jie-fang.github.io/blog/basics-of-ricing" class="text-blue-500" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ricing</a>, hardware mods, gaming, <a href="https://odysee.com/@mattdoestech726:5" class="text-blue-500" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">creating Odysee exclusive content</a>, and coding personal projects. I'm dedicated to becoming a <a href="/assets/GUIDE.txt" class="text-blue-500" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pentester</a>, and I am currently exploring more around the stacks in persuit of my goal.
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold my-6">
      Extras
    </h1>
    <OtherLinks/>
  </div>
</section>
